  "original_title": "\u0db4\u0dc5\u0db8\u0dd4 \u0dc1\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0dda\u0dab\u0dd2\u0dba\u0da7 \u0dc3\u0dd2\u0dc3\u0dd4\u0db1\u0dca \u0d87\u0dad\u0dd4\u0dc5\u0dad\u0dca \u0d9a\u0dd2\u0dbb\u0dd3\u0db8\u0dda \u0d85\u0dba\u0daf\u0dd4\u0db8\u0dca\u0db4\u0dad\u0dca \u0d9a\u0dcf\u0dbd\u0dba \u0daf\u0dd2\u0d9c\u0dd4 \u0d9a\u0dbb\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The application period for admission of students to first grade is extended",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "For the year 2023, it has been arranged to extend the application dates for admission of children to the first grade of schools.",
        "The ministry says that due to the problematic situation in the country, requests are being received from parents to extend the deadline for submitting applications for the enrollment of students in the first grade of 2023.",
        "Accordingly, the Ministry of Education has extended the last date for submission of applications to 01.08.2022."
      ],
